<br>
Unfortunately, I think you are going to have to stay away from them as much as possible, because when you see them together, you are going to get angry and jealous. If you see her alone, you are going to just watch her and fall deeper in love.  If you see *him* alone you're probably going to just look at him and smoulder.<br>
<br>
The only thing I think you can do is stay away from them .. I'm sorry to hear that it's affecting you this way .. there's not much to say. I've had my share of crushes and none of them have ever worked out ... <br>
<br>
I know I had a crush on a friend of a friend and it really hurt when I saw him, at any time, because I knew it wouldn't work out - even though I wanted it to.<br>
<br>
I don't know, in your situation, if it could work out ... but I hope it does for you ... in the mean time, don't pine for her too much, even though I know it will be difficult .. I think I still have a picture of the guy I had the crush on when I was in school...<br>
<br>
Good luck!<br>
