<br>
The best thing to do that I've found is to stay occupied with other things.  Stay away from your friend &amp; the girl...  Meet other people, do other things &amp; make different friends.  Keep yourself occupied.<br>
<br>
After you have given yourself some time away from them, you will be able to view this from a distance &amp; without most of the emotions tied up into it.  It will allow you to logically view it instead of emotionally.<br>
<br>
By staying near them, you are just hurting yourself.  If you try to do anything about it, then you will just be hurting them, &amp; from which the way you sound will just cause you hurt all over again.<br>
